"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-19-soap-legend-olympia-valance-pregnant-miscarriage-twins-21446890\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Former Neighbours star Olympia Valance has confirmed she is pregnant following the miscarriage of twins.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 104, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_Valance\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympia Valance\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_Valance\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_Valance\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The star, 31,is in a relationship with AFL star Thomas Bellchambers.\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 174, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 145, \"end\": 148, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9991470832408244, \"rank\": 0.0005030243652583468, \"text\": \"AFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Football_League\"}, {\"begin\": 154, \"end\": 160, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9999999754104468, \"rank\": 2.456112896521765e-08, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took toInstagramto share the wonderful news, but admitted to her followers that this journey has not been easy.\", \"from\": 175, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After four years of infertility struggles which included the miscarriage of twins, Olympia admitted she had hit her pregnancy away for five and a half months, 'to make sure this wasn't all a dream.'\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 490, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999995422050372, \"rank\": 4.5779518533490755e-07, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: 'But you kept growing and growing and it's starting to look like our dreams have finally come true.\", \"from\": 492, \"to\": 601, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been as open and honest as I could about our struggles with infertility and I truly believed that this day wasn't going to be possible for us.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'So when I saw this positive pregnancy test I have to admit, at the time, I wasn't jumping for joy.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 852, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was full of fear because that's all I have known.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 904, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But as the weeks kept going by it was hard to wipe the smile off our faces.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 980, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  'To the little one we never thought we'd meet, we can not wait to hold you in our arms.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.31441951667815e-18, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7072676445246437e-16, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You were worth every tear, every setback, and every prayer.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To all the people who supported us through the darkest days, thank you.\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know I would not have made it to this point without the strength of my family and friends who managed to hold me up when I was falling apart.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: 'It is also incredibly important for me to recognise that although this is the best news in the world for Thomas and I, my heart aches for anyone that sees this and feels pain.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9999999754104468, \"rank\": 2.456112896521765e-08, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was so hard for me to write this because it feels like I am caught between two worlds.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'It's not an easy road and I would not wish it upon my worst enemy.\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's one hell of an emotional roller coaster.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay strong, keep fighting, but most importantly do not forget to be kind to yourself.'\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1962, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympia, best known for her role as Paige Smith in Australian soap Neighbours,opened up about miscarrying twins in an emotional message last year.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999995422050372, \"rank\": 4.5779518533490755e-07, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\"}, {\"begin\": 2000, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paige Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paige_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9977427691090246, \"rank\": 0.0012669219374793518, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neighbours\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Neighbours\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neighbours\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neighbours\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Thomas and I miscarried twins, right in the middle of Covid, which as you can imagine was excruciatingly painful', she said in a post online.\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"score\": 0.9999999754104468, \"rank\": 2.456112896521765e-08, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Wayne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a loyal Metro Soaps reader, we want to make sure you never miss our articles when searching for stories.\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2363, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have all the latest soaps news, spoilers, videos, and interviews, with a vibrant community of highly engaged readers.\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2484, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click the button below and tickMetro.co.ukto ensure you see stories from us first in Google Search.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2571, \"end\": 2584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Search\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Add us as a Preferred Source  Now you can ensure you never miss a story from the Soaps team  'Since then, we have not been able to conceive.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2727, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That would be two years of really trying.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2769, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For any woman or couple trying to get pregnant, there is no worse pain than every month looking down at that negative pregnancy test.\", \"from\": 2770, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your heart breaks in two.'\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After also speaking about how she currently does not want to go down the IVF route, due to the increase in hormones, she concluded: 'I want babies and I will do everything in my power to get them.'\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3005, \"end\": 3008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/In_vitro_fertilisation\", \"score\": 0.9999999999786269, \"rank\": 2.134398170398133e-11, \"text\": \"IVF\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/In_vitro_fertilisation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/In_vitro_fertilisation\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Understandably, Olympia received many kind and wonderful comments on the post.\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3147, \"end\": 3154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympia_London\", \"score\": 0.9999995422050372, \"rank\": 4.5779518533490755e-07, \"text\": \"Olympia\", \"types\": [\"Q4117